item.title: First session with Dane Dormio
item.description: 11:54 Wednesday 22 May 2019 JST I just finished a two hour session with Dane Dormio, during which we got a high level look at how I am doing in different areas of my life versus how I want to be doing in those areas. Then identified some action and habit I can implement in the next week. Action: clear space for new printer Habit: continue exercises from A Course in Miracles
